text.enText:
In the summer, we have the CBC Award and the 
St. Urus S. to look forward to.

text.jpText:
サクラバクシンオーは他生徒の
お手本となるべく、気合いを入れて
夏合宿に挑むのだった。
text.enText:
Sakura Bakushin-o was determined to be a 
good role model for the other students, and 
she was ready to take on the challenge of 
the summer camp.
